line_1: At every word he spoke, he smil'd at-ween,
line_2: Of middle age he was, if right I ween,

line_1: At every word he spoke, he smil'd at-ween,
line_2: Ne seemed he to taste of dol'rous teen,

line_1: At every word he spoke, he smil'd at-ween,
line_2: Ne wrinkle deep was on his forehead seen,
